import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Stack } from '@mui/material';
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';

import "./ResultPage.scss";

const width = window.innerWidth;
const height = (width <= 479 ? window.innerHeight - 175 : window.innerHeight - 215) + "px";

const ResultPage = () => {

    ////// Translate
    const { t } = useTranslation();

    return (
        <>

<Box className="s-home-5">
                <Box className="s-home-content">
                    <Container>
                        <Box className="s-form-content">
                            <Box sx={{ width: "100%", minHeight: height, }}>
                                <Box className="b-card-3">
                                    <Typography className="b-title">Section 1</Typography>
                                    <Typography className="b-desc">{t('wh_result_desc')}</Typography>
                                </Box>
                                <Grid container spacing={1.5}>
                                    <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                                        <Box className="b-card-5">
                                            <Stack direction="row">
                                                <Box>1</Box>
                                                <Box>Desktop </Box>
                                            </Stack>
                                            <Box>CPU HP 280 PRO G9; Core I5-12500, Ddram 8GB, SSD 256; HDD 1TB</Box>
                                            <Box>Safety Standard: 0</Box>
                                            <Box>In Stock: 1</Box>
                                            <Box>Status: OK</Box>
                                        </Box>
                                    </Grid>
                                </Grid>
{/* 
                                <Box className="s-bot">
                                    <ButtonPrimary title={t('btn_confirm')} handleClick={handleClick} name="pass" />
                                </Box> */}
                            </Box>
                        </Box>
                    </Container>
                </Box>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default ResultPage;
